metadata.name: ORANG- HANTU
metadata.description:
FIRST BUYER OF PICTURED SCULPTURE 'ORANG- HANTU’ (2016) RECEIVES THIS 1/1 NFT (2023). 

PICTURED SCULPTURE - RESIN PIECE CONTAINING UNANALYSED HAIR SAMPLE OF UNKNOWN SPECIES FROM THE SUMATRAN JUNGLE AND DIRT COLLECTED FROM SUSPECTED FOOTPRINT OF THE ORANG PENDEK. 
SEED NECKLACE FROM ANAK DALAM TRIBE.

 SAMPLE COLLECTION DOCUMENTED ON ‘ON THE YETI TRAIL’ DOCUMENTARY. 
EXHIBITED AT ROYAL ACADEMY OF THE ARTS EXHIBITION, PICCADILLY. 

NFT TO BE SOLD SEPARATELY.
